Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆一行人在旅途中的某个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入了一个女孩的梦境中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的名字叫史泰拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身体似乎也受到了卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于巴隆他们的踊跃相助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明白了生存的真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后一行人来到了终年积雪的斯顿雪域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:04.47,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(371,252)}激战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:04.47,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,378)}魔之山脊 -前篇-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:11.86,biaozhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯顿雪域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就冻成这样的话是没办法翻过这座山的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去泡温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 温泉 去吧去吧 马上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉的话 也可以治疗鬼手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说 泡温泉 消百病嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶快行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给我找温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说机器人是倾注了爱心的结晶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方还有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被班图族袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西全都被洗劫一空了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我要泼冷水 你们还是下山的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是膜拜斯顿雪域远古山神的部族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快呀 找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它好像找到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 会不会是温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人倒在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子 我们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子里 村子里来了一群怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 没时间跟你解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干什么 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要求救 却掉到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救救村子里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是班图族的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个袭击旅人的班图族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族才不会做那种没品的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族可是非常有自豪感的部族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定是你想的那样 是被雪崩冲垮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 才不是什么雪崩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯 你注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 右边有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边有三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是四个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击他们的 是你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是村民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 搞错了 这些人是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下你一个人 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些人救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是班图族的族长 奥尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙你们关照小妹 在此谢过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然路过顺便而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么 这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 被雪崩冲垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯顿雪域最近经常这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪崩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧 果然是雪崩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上 村里的不速之客是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心 那只是温泉调查团而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的其他人现在正陪他们在视察周围的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么可担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也赶快下山去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座山对外来者说很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点找到温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为又变冷了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 我果然还是觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还是去看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们上哪儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是让人在意啊 稍微去看一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说 要是找温泉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去问一下刚才的那些人为好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 还有这一招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有脑袋的家伙就是聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是旧的矿场吧 大伙在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 好好听我说 敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔卡 快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃走的话都是这个下场 给我好好记牢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 温泉在什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁松大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死了 出现逃跑者之后又有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 快逃吧 这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁松 为何如此喧闹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这些人的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识他吗 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克 你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:12:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你到这里来干什么 鬼剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我们只是为了能够泡上温泉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼剑士 就问你一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那身手能不能为我们效力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保住小命的话 这是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没办法和你们这些 到处欺凌弱小的家伙好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这个手臂和你们的可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你是要与我们为敌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护这里是我们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉德大陆将会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不变的东西就让它消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于自身的考虑 还是不要抵抗的为好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的话就会和那个鬼剑士同样下场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手 快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对巴隆做那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要走到什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 走你的路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得觉得这么热 原来是这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在这种地方在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们闹出什么骚乱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族的尸体就会增加的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些 已经没有什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟把这些东西藏在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个 玩具啊玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 这个不能拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 好好干活的话就还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 太好了 我很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人们和小孩虽然被抓住了但是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们作为人质 任意驱使我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是没能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是族长吧 帮我们干点活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再靠近这座山了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克 费丽亚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经充分成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热 这样一个劲地加热打算干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 他们怕冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能的把伤者带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人 请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一会 一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族不是自豪感很强的一族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥丢掉了班图族的自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不相信哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴被作为人质抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护部族 我只有变成魔鬼丢掉灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别偷懒 让它烧得更旺些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 难得的客人啊 请好好干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变热了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是红色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽梅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种力量的谜题解开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉德大陆就会改变 一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个神奇的花就是他们拼命的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下来 巴隆
